data.description: Very well taken care of in the beautiful Redwood Place of Legacy in North Bossier.  Spacious home at 1548 sf and fully fenced backyard.  NO CARPET.  Current owner placed brand new wood look tile floors in the main living area and all bedrooms. Excellent schools, community pool, playground, ponds and even walking trails make this area the perfect place to call home.
